[It would be helpful to obtain information on the above data
regarding "lack of immunity." Are repeated cases seen in animals
affected in the previous year, or rather in unaffected, probably
young susceptible animals? In BTV enzootic countries, repeated cases
may indicate the possible involvement of a heterologous serotype. - Mod. AS]
